lessons.content:
JSON 自由 = 兩面刃。前端傳「年齡是字串」、後端期待「年齡是數字」就會壞。**Schema** 是寫給機器看的合約：「資料長這樣才合法」。

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["name", "age"],
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "properties": {
    "name": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1,
      "maxLength": 50
    },
    "age": {
      "type": "integer",
      "minimum": 0,
      "maximum": 150
    },
    "email": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "email"
    },
    "role": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": ["admin", "user", "guest"]
    },
    "tags": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": { "type": "string" },
      "minItems": 1,
      "maxItems": 10,
      "uniqueItems": true
    }
  }
}
```


### 常用驗證關鍵字


| 類型 | 關鍵字 |
| --- | --- |
| 共用 | type, enum, const, required, default, examples |
| string | minLength, maxLength, pattern, format（email/uri/date-time/uuid） |
| number | minimum, maximum, exclusiveMinimum, multipleOf |
| array | items, minItems, maxItems, uniqueItems, contains |
| object | properties, required, additionalProperties, patternProperties |
| 組合 | allOf, anyOf, oneOf, not, if/then/else |


### 進階：條件式 schema

```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "role": { "enum": ["admin", "user"] }
  },
  "if": {
    "properties": { "role": { "const": "admin" } }
  },
  "then": {
    "required": ["permissions"]
  },
  "else": {
    "not": { "required": ["permissions"] }
  }
}
// admin 才需要 permissions 欄位
```


JSON Schema 是業界標準。OpenAI、Anthropic 的 tool use、OpenAPI / Swagger 背後都是它。

**☕ 用人話講**

JSON Schema 是**用一份「規格」描述「這份 JSON 該長怎樣」**——哪些欄位必填、是什麼型別、數字範圍多少。收到資料先拿規格一比，不合格就擋下。**一句話記住**：像報名表的「填寫須知」——姓名必填、電話要 10 碼、年齡得是數字；不照規矩填，直接退件不收。

